snippet.title: Demonetisation 36th Day: People Across India Queue Up Outside Cashless Banks and ATMs

localized.description:
Watch India TV's special report on Demonetisation 36th Day from Ahmedabad. Hundreds of crores have been seized in income tax raids across the country after demonetisation. On the other hand people are struggling to withdraw cash even after waiting for hours in queues outside banks and ATMs.
